original_title: Tootsie's Orchid Lounge: Where the Music Began
overview: The show tells the story of a group of songwriters who hung out together at the bar 30 years ago and who penned some of America's most popular music.
tagline: Willie Nelson hosts an all-star program celebrating Nashville's legendary Tootsie's Orchid Lounge.
title: Tootsie's Orchid Lounge: Where the Music Began
